  "action_title": "<i>Crassula helmsii</i>: Use a combination of control measures",
  "key_messages": "Key Messages:\n\nOne before-and-after study at a single pond in the UK\u00a0found covering Crassula helmsii with carpet, followed by treatment with the herbicide glyphosate, killed 80% of the plant."
}

{
